## Running the tests

Supertest are used for testing endpoints.

```
npm run test
```

### Test example

```
describe('GET Nearby Weather', () => {
    it('returns 200 OK', (done) => {
      request(app)
        .get('/nearby?lat=50&lon=70')
        .set('Accept', 'application/json')
        .expect(200, done);
    });
```

